oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Welcome to California
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Ozanian, Charles
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: I do want to welcome all of you to the meeting. This city is unique because of its beautiful sights. If you go up to about the fortieth or fiftieth floor and look around, you can see Berkeley Hill, etc. The Golden State is a beautiful area to be in. I always enjoy it. I was married in San Francisco and I always look forward to coming back from L.A. Many people from Los Angeles just fly up here to have dinner and fly back, so that's how good the food is here! I imagine you people have seen this the last few nights.
